Title: timesyncd: Crash (Cannot render negative timespan)
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1629451553
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0p10

The check would crash when host time and server time
ran out of sync.

Negative timespans are now detected and result in a {CRIT}
state and an informational message.
